<plot>JUST SAY IT explores the bizarre and hilarious nature of people's number one fear: public speaking. It examines the history and psychology of this fear while following Luke King, the film's director, as he takes a public speaking class and attends Ontario's largest provincial speech competition for kids. Just Say It! features candid interviews with Canadian celebrities including the CBC's Peter Mansbridge, George Chuvalo and the cast of the Royal Canadian Air Farce as they attempt to help Luke shed some light on Canadians' deepest fear.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?282468</url></doc>
